Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.26,0:00:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stars are sometimes good to see, I guess it's the same for the criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soon we'll solve this magical murder mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan and Heiji figure out the trick and solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing the one and only truth with a body of a kid but the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we felt the same light the moment we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, lots and lots of the same emotions filled our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although the signals you sent destroyed my theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These feelings were always beyond your reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let's fight, go against our morals...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And aim for a wider world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, glimmering star, shine over us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, we won't lose the dreams we had when we were young...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care if this town changes someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing I don't want to change is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, glimmering star, shine over us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, we won't lose the dreams we had when we were young...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing I don't want to change is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are invited by legendary magician Hoshikawa Dogo\Nto the house of the famous magician Mr. Masakage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because today is exactly 10 years after Mr. Masakage disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:02:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,some pupil magicians gathered, and one of them, Tenko Himemiya, was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's been about 30 minutes since she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we were with Hoshikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the archives room. It contains the collections of our master, Mr. Masakage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is "Chrismas Tree Magic". This chrismas\Ntree was at the place where Tenko died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this picture, Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's his pupils when they were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, a difference in the shadow of the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of the vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, the moonlight comes from the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the power failure, the moonlight comes from the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that? The moon can't move that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of the vase...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan and Heiji Reasoning Magic\NSolving part
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moonlight and a vase...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that mean. It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe, at first, it was cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:40.47,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Dogo Hoshikawa (27)\Nmagician
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After power failure. the clouds disappeared find we could see the shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That could be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear any voices or the sound of a criminal running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:04:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we were crying. It was dark and frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hoshikawa talked to us, and calmed us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talked to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It's alright. Don't worry. I'm with you, he said over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's really reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please show me the room Handa was sleeping in, just to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:31.23,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,350)}Handa Riki (41)\N{\fs15} magician
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha, you stay in here with Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm irritated because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:59.83,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: Yaiteru means to be jealous or to get sunburned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's YAITERU.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,YAITERU? He didn't get sunburned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... I didn't mean sunburned..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the room you stayed in when you were Mr Masakage is pupil?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bed they used was thrown away 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:20.12,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Masakage Mari (54)\N{\fs14} Wife of Mr. Masakage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the power failure occurred, where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Riki was lying on that sofa when I opened the door. He didn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was dark, so I said we shouldn't move until we could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who fixed the breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was me. I was near the breaker with Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room is under the archive room. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one could get out that small window.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think this house has some trick, because it was designed by a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no elevator that could have lifted up Tenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mari and Handa were here, so the murderer\Ncouldn't have killed Tenko in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hoshikawa was being held by Kazuha, so he couldn't have moved Tenko's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, the murderer must have come from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We inspected that shrubbery. We found broken branches and a footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That shrubbery is under Mr. Masakage's room.\NHattori, maybe what you said is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal hide in the archive room, planted her body in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,entered Mr. Masakage's room, then escaped out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK. Let's investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the criminal came from outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest is police work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. It's not. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? You found the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I found the criminal who killed Tenko and hid the trick he used.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will show you now, Can I use a thin policeman and a fat policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thin and Fat? Ok, then Takagi and Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but what are you going to do? Is it a dangerous trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Just help me a little, ok? It's good\Nto worry about your subordinates but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alright Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's, it's alright. Tenko disappeared and was found after 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take everyone to the corridor on the second\Nfloor, and maybe you'll be surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you were saying, right Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I will call Takagi and Chiba to this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Handa Mari, please go another room and wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, please get Hoshikawa and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ok, we will go to the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? We gathered everyone because you already figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no. I figured out why I get irritated when I think about Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm... I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will all now enter the stage where we will solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, the murderer is here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:10:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you said that the murderer who killed Tenko came from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer came to steal Mr. Masakage's magic file in archive room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Tenko saw him, so he killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Hoshikawa, Ran, and Kazuha came, so he put\NTenko in the corridor, entered Mr. Masakage's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and jumped out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is also a switch that caused the power failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Handa and Mari were in the room on the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hoshikawa was with Ran and Kazuha. So, who\Ntook Tenko and how did the person do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mari said that a weird man came here 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man may be a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did that man have any distinct habits?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A habit? Hmmm... I can't remember. It was 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example. a habit where he adjusted his sunglasses with his left little finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! He had that habit. ...Ah!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know something, Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but I can guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mari is talking about the man in this photo with the cap and mustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couuld he be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Handa in his youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:12:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Mr. Handa has the habit of adjusting this sunglasses with his left little finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the man that Ms. Mari met 5 years ago was Mr. Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot. If that man was Mr. Handa, she would have noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know when somebody lies, they think about a model. To make it seem real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The model is a young Mr. Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So the man's habit was like Mr. Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we don't doubt Ms. Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:13:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of where Tenko was and the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she knows that Hoshikawa is the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Ms. Mari was protecting Hoshikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? I was hanging onto him when we found Tenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will solve that trick now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See this corridor'? It's the same as it was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, It was like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is dark, but I can see there is nothing at the end of this corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's more, I was holding Hoshikawa's arm like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, you're grabbing too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let you cheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on, explain the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah. when Hoshikawa turned on this switch, a power failure occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fix the breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop joking. You must have come out from the archives when it was dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I was in here. The door was not opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't see Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,AAAAAAAAhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it? Conan ...Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji just moved the door of Mr. Masakage's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Hoshikawa did in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohhh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This hallway is identical to the end of the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This closet is like the archive room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The left-hand wall is a screen and.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The small window at the end of the corridor is\Na large window half hidden by this cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door to Mr. Masakage's room is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The back of Mr. Masakage's door is a mirror. Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whet you saw before the power failure occurred is the inside of this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the body was planted at the end of the corridor from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. When the power failure occurred Hoshikawa closed this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we entered that room, the back of the door wasn't a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there wasn't a strange door like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This door is designed well. It can combine and become one ordinary door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this door too thick This line is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yea. and also, Kazuha and Ran noticed the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said before, the shadow of the vase changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.14,Signs,,0,0,0,,Before Tenko Found
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.14,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,0)}After Tenko found
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remembered, and I am convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were different places before Tenko was found and after Tenko was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this house is really tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. Mr. Masakage designed this house to do this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would bring guests to this corridor. and make\NChristmas trees appear to surprise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Ms. Mari immediately realized that Hoshikawa was the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the person who invited us here was Mr. Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, Hoshikawa didn't have the will to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was when Tenko said she was going to perform "Return of the Witch".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. At first, that show was called "Return of the Devil".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Masakage thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has the same setting and direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She stole our master's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that magic is too dangerous to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she only wanted to steal the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for her to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We decided not to show this magic before she became the pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Hoshikawa protected me and said "the file is in the archive room".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in fact, he had always had the idea written down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10 years ago. he said "I forgot that notebook,\NI must go fund it "but he never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:19:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wondered how she saw that notebook I called\Nher to our master's room and asked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:10.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I stole it. I'm pretty dexterous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will return it if he comes back. I don't think he'll ever be so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he may retire because he didn't notice I stole his notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think he will be happy if I perform his unpublished magic to the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I wasn't thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came to, I found her dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remembered the master's "christmas tree" magic, and used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, you broke branches and left a footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the murder weapon is that vase. There is blood in the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Hoshikawa's clothing is stained with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The proof is everywhere. I am not very good as a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are not good because you are not a magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your crime will not disappear like magicians do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:21:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's stop the time and hold me tight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to be close
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I loved you so many times
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crying till the dawn comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your warmth makes it painful
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fearing that I lose my hair when you touch me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This attraction makes us closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will find out what tries to tear us apart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,stop the time and smile softly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will be on your side forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,light of the dawn shine on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and let us shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What great deduction, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.35,0:22:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your reasoning may be better than Kudo's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you think so too? Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember something that Heiji said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.43,0:22:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I am irritated when Kazuha us with other men".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ehh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I understand that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.75,0:22:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ehhhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe, maybe I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ehhhhhh? Stop it, Heiji. Everyone is watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you are my follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A follower That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A leader feels bad when his follower has fun with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.07,0:23:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I was irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I your follower?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your father is a follower of my father. So you are a follower of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That night, Ran sent me a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,PS. Shinichi, do you think I am your follower?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. now...
